data.description: Back on the market - buyers financing fell through. Introducing this wonderful 3-bed, 2-bath home with a den which could be easily converted to 4th bedroom. 1600 sq ft of living space on a 5502 sq ft lot, this home has a lot to offer. The interior is bright and inviting, and the kitchen is fully equipped with modern appliances. The primary bedroom features its own bathroom, offering a peaceful retreat. Outside, you'll find a huge screened patio, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The location is super convenient, with easy access to amenities and major roads. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your new home! Roof 2016, HVAC 2021, water heater 2020.
